            <description><![CDATA[【正处高发期！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%86%E7%94%B2%E6%B5%81%E5%92%8C%E6%99%AE%E9%80%9A%E6%84%9F%E5%86%92%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%86%E7%94%B2%E6%B5%81%E5%92%8C%E6%99%AE%E9%80%9A%E6%84%9F%E5%86%92%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#如何区分甲流和普通感冒#</span></a>？<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[感冒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_ganmao-286fc59b6d.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】当前我国流感病毒活动水平有所增强，以甲流为主。①<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%94%B2%E6%B5%81%E7%9A%84%E7%97%87%E7%8A%B6%E6%AF%94%E6%99%AE%E9%80%9A%E6%84%9F%E5%86%92%E6%9B%B4%E9%87%8D%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%94%B2%E6%B5%81%E7%9A%84%E7%97%87%E7%8A%B6%E6%AF%94%E6%99%AE%E9%80%9A%E6%84%9F%E5%86%92%E6%9B%B4%E9%87%8D%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#甲流的症状比普通感冒更重#</span></a>。②甲流与新冠叠加感染的概率低。③不宜自行服用奥司他韦，需遵医嘱。④接种流感疫苗是最有效的预防手段。小卫带你9图速览甲流防治👇🏻（人民日报） <img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hbixoemfnmj20j617ktdu.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hbixof21f2j20j61cf0y5.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hbixofdww4j20j60yfq6i.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hbixo0xbfpj20j615ktdf.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hbixofvi3zj20j60m7wgm.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hbixogajtkj20j617ydl3.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hbixogs2ydj20j615kgq3.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30